729799f-a.title: Richmond: Van Duzer Street - William Street
729799f-a.text:
292 Van Duzer Street, at the S.W. corne of William
Street (right), showing the home of the Democratic Club. The
house was owned by Dr. W. C. Anderson in 1874; by Karl Kapff
from 1898 to 1907, and by A. Sommers in 1917. Dates refer to
maps on which the owners' names appear.
May 25, 1235
P. L. Sperr
